                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-154-off927 t18320405-154-cd928"></join>, 4 handkerchiefs, value 14s.; 1 pair of stockings, value 4s.; 1 ring, value 12s.; 1 seal, value 25s.; 1 key, value 5s.; 3 breast-pins, value 12s, and 1 brooch, value 2s.
